{"tid":1695002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林奠：對受傷科大生和其他受傷市民表示深切慰問 望早日康復","createTime":"2019-11-05T11:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:11:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"97213c5c28b636b90f6e4f0e3da0de3098092d3a","tid":1695002,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"【18:40】正在外訪的特首林鄭月娥傍晚在上海見記者，<span style=\"color: red;\">對受傷科大生及其他在衝突中受傷的市民表示深切慰問，希望他們早日康復</span>。她表示，警方非常重視科大生受傷事件，已將案件交重案組調查，外界目前不宜對事件妄下定論。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥稱，近期每次集會示威都演變成「極端暴行」，呼籲所有市民遠離有關場合，「令警方執法時不會產生不必要誤會」。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人陳淑莊表示，大家都關心受傷的科大學生，她指出事件是發生在警暴的現場，林鄭月娥是有權的人，亦是令香港情況不斷惡化的人，除了表達關心，林太有很多東西可做，以避免同類狀况，而《禁蒙面法》幫不上忙。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191105/s00001/1572940878754/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00001%2F1572940878754%2F&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=502be278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00001%2F1572940878754%2F&h=b02bad1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191105/s00001/1572940878754/</a>"},{"pid":"92fda5e500677ff8de0644d13a71c64462add6dd","tid":1695002,"uid":285371,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"唔洗提啲垃圾了"},{"pid":"32a5f3b87149cb53b2195d685b76ee871d4396d3","tid":1695002,"uid":19363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"有咩資格？<br />\n貓哭老鼠"},{"pid":"f57e47d1664eefd9261b334d2365c46103ecade2","tid":1695002,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"攬炒報仇"},{"pid":"9b68cfcfe57408cfb9708fdbc7fb8d0d0e9d3cac","tid":1695002,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20